    "status" : "extensions",
    "div" : "<div xml:lang=\"fr-FR\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" lang=\"fr-FR\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : EnsembleValeurs jdv-famille-id-cisis</b></p><a name=\"jdv-famille-id-cisis\"> </a><a name=\"hcjdv-famille-id-cisis\"> </a><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">version : 10; Dernière mise à jour : 2026-06-22 13:58:56+0200; Langue : fr-FR</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profil: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/shareablevalueset.html\">Shareable ValueSet</a></p></div><ul><li>Include ce(s) code(s) tel qu'il(s) est (sont) défini(s) dans <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-v3-RoleCode.html\"><code>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-RoleCode</code></a><span title=\"La version est explicitement indiquée comme étant 4.0.0\"> version &#x1F4CD;4.0.0</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Affichage</b></td><td><b>Définition</b></td></tr><tr><td><code>DAU</code></td><td>Fille</td><td>The player of the role is a female offspring of the scoping entity (parent).</td></tr><tr><td><code>PGRMTH</code></td><td>Grand-mère paternelle</td><td>**Description:**The player of the role is the biological mother of the scoping person's biological father.</td></tr><tr><td><code>MGRMTH</code></td><td>Grand-mère maternelle</td><td>**Description:**The player of the role is the biological mother of the scoping person's biological mother.</td></tr><tr><td><code>MTH</code></td><td>Mère</td><td>The player of the role is a female who conceives, gives birth to, or raises and nurtures the scoping entity (child).</td></tr><tr><td><code>SIS</code></td><td>Sœur</td><td>The player of the role is a female sharing one or both parents in common with the scoping entity.</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
